# NovaReign: The Sovereign Intelligence Economic Engine

## Architect: Chelsea Woods
**Lead Systems Architect | Pioneer of Arch-Agent Methodology**

NovaReign is a decentralized, autonomous multi-agent ecosystem engineered for wealth generation and recursive system optimization. Moving beyond traditional "Chat-AI," NovaReign utilizes **Arch-Agents**—self-healing entities capable of monitoring market variables and executing complex code repairs without human intervention.

