## 🛠 Methodology & Inventions
### 1. Arch-Agent Autonomy
The implementation of "Ghost Recon" monitoring protocols allows agents to operate in a state of constant surveillance, identifying and neutralizing threats before they impact the economic engine.

### 2. Forensic Resolution Logic
A proprietary decision-making framework that analyzes the "Why" behind data inputs to architect solutions that ensure long-term strategic clarity and market dominance.

### 3. Self-Healing Recursive Loops
Agent Zero continuously audits the system's codebase, automatically generating and testing patches within containerized environments to ensure 99.9% uptime for the wealth-generation engine.

